    "description": "Sokoramp is a Sokoban based puzzle game that adds several mechanics to the core gameplay. <br><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use ramps to navigate over boxes<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766440/extras/29fe889fc7fa385d77f246d2a050b620.webp?t=1635845304\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766440/extras/29fe889fc7fa385d77f246d2a050b620.poster.avif?t=1635845304\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=224 /></picture></span><br><br></li><li> Touch color coded squares in the right order<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766440/extras/6a7e2dfa1308b5cca0f6a852c853ec14.webp?t=1635845304\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766440/extras/6a7e2dfa1308b5cca0f6a852c853ec14.poster.avif?t=1635845304\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=224 /></picture></span><br><br></li><li> Unlock regions<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766440/extras/766d70f8647c56ccb756e557438c44e3.webp?t=1635845304\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766440/extras/766d70f8647c56ccb756e557438c44e3.poster.avif?t=1635845304\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=224 /></picture></span><br></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  50 original levels with increasing difficulty<br></li><li>  4 worlds, each with extra graphical effects accessible via a cheat code hidden in the game<br></li><li>  3 bonus levels, unlockable by solving the 50 base levels in close to the perfect amount of steps</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Usability Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Full Screen/Windowed mode<br></li><li>  Resolution settings<br></li><li>  